quote.nm: Xingye Wulian Service Group Co. Ltd.
quote.summary: Xingye Wulian Service Group Co Ltd is an investment holding company mainly engaged in property management services. Property Management and Value-added Services provides a wide range of property management services which include, among others, security, cleaning, greening and gardening, parking space management, repair and maintenance for common areas and customer services, and value-added services which include repair and maintenance for exclusive use areas, renovation waste clearance, intermediary leasing services, and others. Property Engineering Services provides customers with property engineering services which include the planning, design and installation of security and surveillance systems, access control systems, carpark management systems and construction site management systems, in order to enhance the quality of the property management systems of our customers. It also includes the Property Development segment and the Others segment.
